  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/d90cc77d08a0ab9ceed35b88ce1bdc4b.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/d90cc77d08a0ab9ceed35b88ce1bdc4b.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/d90cc77d08a0ab9ceed35b88ce1bdc4b.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The NecroDancer's back in an all-new rhythm game! Dragged into a strange new world, Cadence must engage in musical combat with monsters pouring through the Rift! Each monster has unique behaviors—like bats that shift lanes when attacked—and tougher foes take multiple hits to dispatch. Learn the pattern of each new fretful fiend to keep the music flowing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/9b3e9b4973ee53c78b60cd1e6c8f9a42.avif?t=1773246624\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras_big/9b3e9b4973ee53c78b60cd1e6c8f9a42.avif?t=1773246624 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Showstopping Music:</strong> Brand new soundtrack with 40+ Rhythm Rift tracks by Danny Baranowsky, Jules Conroy, Alex Moukala, Josie Brechner, Sam Webster, and Nick Nausbaum with more on the way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficulty that Scales with You:</strong> Four intensity levels for each Rhythm Rift - EASY, MEDIUM, HARD, and IMPOSSIBLE.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race to the Top:</strong> Climb your way to the top of global leaderboards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Music:</strong> Create your own custom beat maps with the actual developer tools our designers use!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Replayability:</strong> Once you’ve conquered our hand-crafted levels, challenge your sight-reading with <strong>Remix Mode</strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remix Mode throws a fresh beatmap your way every playthrough while retaining the original level's rhythmic design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remix mode also makes <strong>DAILY CHALLENGES</strong> possible, by changing up the circumstances for each song. Play the same random seed as every other player that day and see how you rank on global leaderboards!</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/3a83d936a5c273b94542ad904e8f9f57.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/3a83d936a5c273b94542ad904e8f9f57.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/3a83d936a5c273b94542ad904e8f9f57.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/bc2c7e773d68320ce070d420db93b486.avif?t=1773246624\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras_big/bc2c7e773d68320ce070d420db93b486.avif?t=1773246624 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go head to head against five fearsome foes in rhythm-based boss battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/350308857c4286507f63dd866e83da1c.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/350308857c4286507f63dd866e83da1c.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/350308857c4286507f63dd866e83da1c.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/c4faecb0c32017088213db779c14de3e.avif?t=1773246624\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras_big/c4faecb0c32017088213db779c14de3e.avif?t=1773246624 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in Cadence and friends’ modern misadventures through five quirky, slice-of-life rhythm minigames. Take a boppin' yoga class, help a friend with a part-time job, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/5b1c929a3b8ae655b3646fa640aff38d.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/5b1c929a3b8ae655b3646fa640aff38d.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/5b1c929a3b8ae655b3646fa640aff38d.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/d90cc77d08a0ab9ceed35b88ce1bdc4b.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/d90cc77d08a0ab9ceed35b88ce1bdc4b.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/d90cc77d08a0ab9ceed35b88ce1bdc4b.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The NecroDancer's back in an all-new rhythm game! Dragged into a strange new world, Cadence must engage in musical combat with monsters pouring through the Rift! Each monster has unique behaviors—like bats that shift lanes when attacked—and tougher foes take multiple hits to dispatch. Learn the pattern of each new fretful fiend to keep the music flowing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/9b3e9b4973ee53c78b60cd1e6c8f9a42.avif?t=1773246624\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras_big/9b3e9b4973ee53c78b60cd1e6c8f9a42.avif?t=1773246624 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Showstopping Music:</strong> Brand new soundtrack with 40+ Rhythm Rift tracks by Danny Baranowsky, Jules Conroy, Alex Moukala, Josie Brechner, Sam Webster, and Nick Nausbaum with more on the way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficulty that Scales with You:</strong> Four intensity levels for each Rhythm Rift - EASY, MEDIUM, HARD, and IMPOSSIBLE.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race to the Top:</strong> Climb your way to the top of global leaderboards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Music:</strong> Create your own custom beat maps with the actual developer tools our designers use!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Replayability:</strong> Once you’ve conquered our hand-crafted levels, challenge your sight-reading with <strong>Remix Mode</strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remix Mode throws a fresh beatmap your way every playthrough while retaining the original level's rhythmic design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remix mode also makes <strong>DAILY CHALLENGES</strong> possible, by changing up the circumstances for each song. Play the same random seed as every other player that day and see how you rank on global leaderboards!</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/3a83d936a5c273b94542ad904e8f9f57.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/3a83d936a5c273b94542ad904e8f9f57.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/3a83d936a5c273b94542ad904e8f9f57.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/bc2c7e773d68320ce070d420db93b486.avif?t=1773246624\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras_big/bc2c7e773d68320ce070d420db93b486.avif?t=1773246624 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go head to head against five fearsome foes in rhythm-based boss battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/350308857c4286507f63dd866e83da1c.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/350308857c4286507f63dd866e83da1c.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/350308857c4286507f63dd866e83da1c.mp4?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/c4faecb0c32017088213db779c14de3e.avif?t=1773246624\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras_big/c4faecb0c32017088213db779c14de3e.avif?t=1773246624 width=800 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in Cadence and friends’ modern misadventures through five quirky, slice-of-life rhythm minigames. Take a boppin' yoga class, help a friend with a part-time job, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/5b1c929a3b8ae655b3646fa640aff38d.poster.avif?t=1773246624\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/5b1c929a3b8ae655b3646fa640aff38d.webm?t=1773246624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073250/extras/5b1c929a3b8